sourcesContent: import mainApi from "../api/mainApi";    export default {        name: "Apps",        data: function () {            return {                appList: [],                dialog: false,                domains: null,                headers: [                    {                        text: 'Applications',                        align: 'left',                        value: 'name'                    },                    { text: 'Id', value: 'Id'},                    { text: 'Status', value: 'Status' },                    { text: 'Creation', value: 'Creation' },                    { text: 'Owner', value: 'Owner' },                    { text: 'Settings', value: 'Settings' }                ],            }        },        methods: {            loadDomains(appName) {                this.$router.push(this.$route.query.redirect || appName);            }        },        created() {            mainApi().get('apps', {})                .then(response => {                    this.appList = response.data.apps;                }).catch(e => {                    throw e;            });        }    }
